text: Heaven and Pancake () is a 1959 Swedish comedy movie directed by Hasse Ekman (who also stars) and starring Sickan Carlsson, Gunnar Björnstrand, Lena Granhagen, Sigge Fürst, Stig Järrel. == Other websites == * Category:1959 comedy movies Category:Swedish comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Hasse Ekman
title: Heaven and Pancake
